Class Student

java.lang.Object
classes.Person
classes.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Student extends Person implements Serializable
Represents a student, extending the Person class. This class includes student-specific attributes such as student ID, enrolled course, optional subject, enrolled class, and a list of student grades. It provides functionality to manage these attributes.
